# VD Advisory Group

> VD Advisory Group is the private diagnostic strategy practice of Veronica Dietz. The firm locates the one load-bearing structural issue generating most of the friction inside a founder-led business, so the founder can stop treating symptoms and restructure the thing actually causing them.

## About the practice

VD Advisory Group works privately and 1:1 with founder-led businesses. The methodology is diagnostic rather than prescriptive. The work focuses on pattern recognition across positioning, offer structure, audience fit, and decision architecture to surface the structural issue creating downstream friction.

Veronica Dietz is the founder. She has nearly a decade of experience in strategic advisory, brand strategy, and diagnostic consulting across clients from early-stage founders to Fortune 500 brands. She is also the founder of Tyche Digital Agency and host of The Aligned Edit podcast (Season 3, weekly).

The practice is based in the Orange County and Las Vegas area and serves clients across the United States.

## Core thesis

Most founders do not have a marketing problem. They have a structural one. Execution without orientation creates expensive cycles. The work is to find the load-bearing issue and name it, so decisions can be made cleanly rather than in isolation.

